Index each slot with a number (starting form 1)
and input index with their length in pair (with 0 0 to stop).
e.g. 1 4 (Enter) -> word 1 requires 4 letters
1 5
2 5
3 10
4 5
5 7
6 6 
7 5
8 5 
9 6
10 8
11 11
0 0
